defaultI am not complacent and will be seeking further opportunities to increase efficiency and improve services during my term in office.  The transfer of funding to Police and Crime Commissioners to commission services for victims offers a real opportunity for us to put victims at the heart of the criminal justice system and ensure that victims no longer fall through the cracks as has happened in the past.  
defaultThrough my engagement with the public
default.  I have been
default informed of cases where victims do not appear to have received an appropriate standard of service from the police or criminal justice partners.  As an elected representative of the people of Cheshire, I have challenged the relevant agency in such cases to ensure that lessons are learnt for the future.
