defaultI believe Commissioners must start driving this agenda now and look beyond regional collaborations which have prevailed in the past.  A good example of looking beyond region
defaultal boundaries is the successful, innovative 
defaultcollaboration between Cheshire and Northamptonshire to deliver back office support functions whilst reducing costs.
